descriptionHtml:
Despite there are lots of excellent textures mods (I use most of them), I made a few (very High Res) just for fun.

These textures are not intended to compete or be realistics. I\'m happy to share if you like this more than those you have. Compatible with flora overhaul.

Are made from scratch. I took some photos from colected leaves, when was necessary.

I recomend installing with NMM, so you can uninstall it easy if you have a problem (as I have so few time for this, won\'t be able to give support).

Please endorse... If people like my work I\'ll keep uploading some more textures.

_________


V1.0 A pair of textures used by some trees and the most common grass in snowed regions.


_________
